{"tid":1643512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"事實係我地而家吹党鐵唔脹，但係我哋話左俾全世界聽，香港人嘅創意同能力係無限嘅","createTime":"2019-10-10T07:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T07:45:40.000Z","uid":330237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4e9059ab1b38e9d0cf4d73f2a44d855f9e558f1e","tid":1643512,"uid":330237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:05:48.000Z","msg":"我地由最初拉緊急制，擋門<br />\n之後識跳閘，幫車飛加料<br />\n直到識幫佢裝修<br />\n呢幾個月黎<br />\n我地不斷學習、不斷進化<br />\n證明左d咩？<br />\n香港人唔單止係一班剩係識ot嘅奴隸<br />\n我地叻到<br />\n有能力對抗世界上最強大嘅極權<br />\n無論個政權出咩招<br />\n我地都有能力拆解<br />\n<br />\n而家党鐵玩埋d陰濕招<br />\n玩封站，扮壞閘機<br />\n自然為是咁撚鳩我地<br />\n你哋唔係咁都忍到呀？<br />\n<br />\n香港人、連登仔<br />\n放完個short break<br />\n係時候轉下個腦<br />\n諗下點解決班懶係醒嘅党鐵高層<br />\n<br />\n小弟不才<br />\n所以開呢個po<br />\n希望同各位手足一齊<br />\n集思廣益。"},{"pid":"48e14288cb76ab7ca2dffa1a8c7dff980559c561","tid":1643512,"uid":330237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:06:17.000Z","msg":"推唔郁"},{"pid":"b7d7feae5e76205de1b6c5b4652256f849db362c","tid":1643512,"uid":330237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:06:30.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"47c1932fc1f958219195b68c69c186ae034d55bc","tid":1643512,"uid":330237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:06:43.000Z","msg":"都係推唔郁"},{"pid":"c809a6211c4914e16d6edbdff8312bd6897192ab","tid":1643512,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:09:36.000Z","msg":"匪共 根本將城管公安 放入曬 香港狗隊<br />\n之前話個犬放假比咗個id人用就係咁解<br />\n成立調查？根本唔會 下一步只會屠城<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B4VgCLjICJY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DB4VgCLjICJY&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em8FcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=b8469ed6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B4VgCLjICJY</a> 清楚的大陸口音「趕緊走了 嘿！」"},{"pid":"12ebd2fb1fe0a62170208d8a6214407d5d62d0c8","tid":1643512,"uid":75877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019